videos.description: 1H (16:29) WAKE Konstantinos Mitoglou made Dunk. Assisted by Bryant Crawford.
videos.headline: K. Mitoglou made Dunk. Assisted by B. Crawford.

videos.description: With the shot clock running down, Wake Forest's Konstantinos Mitoglou drives the lane, but Virginia's Anthony Gill viciously rejects the shot to force the shot clock violation.
videos.headline: That's how you swat a shot with all kinds of authority

videos.description: Wake Forest is looking for the upset over Virginia thanks to Bryant Crawford finishing off a fast break with a huge one-handed slam.
videos.headline: Crawford's tomahawk slam ignites Wake Forest

videos.description: Wake Forest's Devin Thomas cuts between two defenders and throws down a hellacious dunk for the Demon Deacons while getting fouled.
videos.headline: Thomas cuts through defender for monstrous dunk

videos.description: Virginia stuns Wake Forest when Darius Thompson hits a rainbow desperation 3-pointer at the buzzer to cap off a comeback from seven points down in the final seconds to win.
videos.headline: Virginia's buzzer-beater caps incredible comeback
